qgl-demo
A simple demonstration of OpenGL in Qt.
Created for an OpenGL article on
http://www.zez.org

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Copyright (C) 2001 eZ systems as, Norway
(http://www.ez.no)

Released under the GNU General Public License (GPL)
See the file COPYING for details.


----------------------------------------------------------------------
Requirements:
Qt-2.2 and tmake
(Available from www.trolltech.com)
Qt must be compiled with OpenGL enabled.


----------------------------------------------------------------------
Build instructions:
tar -zxf qgl-demo.tar.gz
cd qgl-demo
tmake -o Makefile qgl-demo.pro
make
./qgl-demo


----------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:
Gunnstein Lye <gl@ez.no>

